<bibRefCitation id="E955B2A9FFFD270C64A9FEFD83A491A5" author="Lotters &amp; Schmitz" box="[421,700,367,393]" firstAuthor="Lotters" pageId="42" pageNumber="343" pagination="149 - 154" refId="ref32397" refString="Lotters, S. &amp; Schmitz, A. (2004) A new species of tree frog (Amphibia; Hyperolius) from the Bakossi Mountains, south-west- Cameroon. Bonner zoologische Beitrage, 52, 149 - 154." type="journal article" year="2004">Lötters &amp; Schmitz, 2004</bibRefCitation>
